OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old escaped from HMP
OL,7,FWandsworth in south-west London in
OL,8,FSeptember 2023 by clinging to the
OL,9,Funderside of a food delivery truck,
OL,10,FITV News' Reporter Martha Fairlie has
OL,11,Fthe latest
OL,13,FFormer soldier Daniel Khalife has
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty partway through his
OL,15,Ftrial to escaping from prison under a
OL,16,Ffood truck.
OL,18,FKhalife, 23, changed his plea to a
OL,19,Fcharge of escaping from lawful custody
OL,20,Fhalfway through his trial at Woolwich
OL,21,FCrown Court.
