OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FHe continues to deny the spying and
OL,7,Fterrorism charges against him. The ex-
OL,8,Fsoldier is accused of gathering
OL,9,Finformation for Iran.
OL,11,FKhalife escaped from HMP Wandsworth in
OL,12,Fsouth-west London in September 2023 by
OL,13,Fclinging to the underside of a food
OL,14,Fdelivery truck using a sling made from
OL,15,Fkitchen trousers.
