OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FHe escaped in the hope he would be
OL,7,Fkept in a high-security unit (HSU) at
OL,8,Fa different prison, away from "sex
OL,9,Foffenders" and "terrorists" after his
OL,10,Frecapture, he previously told his
OL,11,Ftrial at Woolwich Crown Court.
OL,13,FMrs Justice Bobbie Cheema-Grubb told
OL,14,Fjurors she had asked Khalife if he
OL,15,Fwanted the prison escape charge to be
OL,16,Fput to him again.
OL,18,FWhen the charge was put to the former
OL,19,Fsoldier, he replied: "I'm guilty."
