OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FThe court heard he planned a fake
OL,7,Fescape attempt for August 21 in the
OL,8,Fhope he would be moved to the HSU, but
OL,9,Fdecided that a genuine escape was his
OL,10,Fonly option after the incident was not
OL,11,Freported to senior prison staff.
OL,13,FKhalife wanted to be kept in the HSU
OL,14,Fat HMP Belmarsh ` a prison within a
OL,15,Fprison holding some of the country's
OL,16,Fmost dangerous criminals ` because he
OL,17,Fbelieved he would be safer there, the
OL,18,Fcourt heard.
