OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FFive days before his successful
OL,7,Fescape, he attached a sling to the
OL,8,Funderside of the lorry made from
OL,9,Fkitchen trousers and carabiners.
OL,11,FThe sling "wasn't spotted at
OL,12,FWandsworth gate or any other prison",
OL,13,FKhalife said.
OL,15,F"When the tail lift raised it covered
OL,16,Fme entirely," he continued.
OL,18,F"If the makeshift sling wasn't
OL,19,Fnoticed, they're hardly going to
OL,20,Fnotice me."
