OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,F"I would do anything to go back to my
OL,7,Fcareer (in the Army)."
OL,9,FWhen asked by the prosecution on
OL,10,FMonday why he did not tell any Army
OL,11,Fcolleagues about his contact with
OL,12,FIran, Khalife said he was "focused" on
OL,13,Fcontacting British intelligence
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,FKhalife has previously claimed he was
OL,17,Fhoping to become a double agent for
OL,18,Fthe UK and said the documents he
OL,19,Fhanded over to Iran were fabricated.
