OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FIn a report published earlier this
OL,7,Fyear, HMP Wandsworth's Independent
OL,8,FMonitoring Board (IMB) ` made up of
OL,9,Fvolunteers tasked by ministers with
OL,10,Fscrutinising conditions in custody `
OL,11,Fsaid an audit found a raft of security
OL,12,Ffailings at the scandal-hit jail in
OL,13,Fthe wake of the escape.
OL,15,FThe IMB said the incident led to
OL,16,Fmultiple reviews and action, including
OL,17,F"previously unavailable funding" being
OL,18,Ffound for security improvements and
OL,19,F"significant investment" in a bid to
OL,20,Fstop "illicit items" being taken into
OL,21,Fthe prison.
